OL,3,CMurder accused denies lying over
OL,4,Cbaby's bath death
OL,6,FA teacher accused of the sexual abuse
OL,7,Fand murder of an adopted baby has
OL,8,Fdenied making up a story that the
OL,9,Fchild drowned in the bath.
OL,11,FJamie Varley, 37, was questioned about
OL,12,Fthe day 13-month-old Preston Davey
OL,13,Fdied after being rushed to hospital by
OL,14,Fhimself and his partner, John McGowan-
OL,15,FFazakerley, 32.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
