FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779642355
OL,3,CMurder accused denies lying over
OL,4,Cbaby's bath death
OL,6,FVarley, at times emotional, said he
OL,7,Fleft the child, who he named Elijah,
OL,8,Fin the bath for only a couple of
OL,9,Fminutes, but returned to find him
OL,10,Fsubmerged, a jury at Preston Crown
OL,11,FCourt heard.
OL,13,FBut a Home Office pathologist later
OL,14,Fruled out drowning and found the child
OL,15,Fhad suffered 40 traumatic injuries
OL,16,Fwhich jurors have been told are
OL,17,Fconsistent with sexual and physical
OL,18,Fabuse.
OL,20,FBoth men deny all charges.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779642355
OL,3,CMurder accused denies lying over
OL,4,Cbaby's bath death
OL,6,FNick Johnson KC, defending Varley,
OL,7,Fcompleted his questions by asking the
OL,8,Fdefendant: "Mr Varley, how do you feel
OL,9,Fnow about Preston Elijah's death?"
OL,11,FVarley replied: "I feel we have not
OL,12,Fbeen given time to grieve. I feel we
OL,13,Fare still looking for our answers.
OL,15,F"I feel our pathologist, Professor
OL,16,FJack Crane, is closer to what I
OL,17,Fexperienced that day.
OL,19,F"I know 100% their allegations and
OL,20,Fopinions and view points are wrong. It
OL,21,Fcould not be further from the truth.
OL,26,@pD@LOUqD@bO]sD@QOUwD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779642355
OL,3,CMurder accused denies lying over
OL,4,Cbaby's bath death
OL,6,F"I'm lost for words."
OL,8,FMr Johnson said: "What would you say,
OL,9,Fif it's said the bath incident is
OL,10,Fentirely made up?"
OL,12,FVarley replied: "It's not. There would
OL,13,Fbe no reason to make such things up."
OL,15,FPreston, described as happy, healthy
OL,16,Fand a "bubby" baby, was adopted and
OL,17,Fbegan living with the defendants at
OL,18,Ftheir home in Blackpool on April 1
OL,19,F2023.
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@UO]pD@ROUrD@RO]tD@QOUuD@eO]xD@
OL,26,AGOUxD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779642355
OL,3,CMurder accused denies lying over
OL,4,Cbaby's bath death
OL,6,FBut it is alleged before his death
OL,7,Ffour months later on July 27, he was
OL,8,Froutinely ill-treated, had indecent
OL,9,Fimages and videos taken of him, and
OL,10,Fwas sexually abused and physically
OL,11,Fassaulted.
OL,13,FVarley, who took parental leave from
OL,14,Fhis job as head of year at a local
OL,15,Fhigh school, said on the afternoon of
OL,16,Fthe day Preston died the child did not
OL,17,Fhave is usual nap so he put him in bed
OL,18,Fwith himself and nodded off.
OL,20,FAfter he woke up he noticed Preston
OL,21,Fwas not well.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779642355
OL,3,CMurder accused denies lying over
OL,4,Cbaby's bath death
OL,6,F"What did you do?" Mr Johnson asked.
OL,8,FVarley replied: "I opened Snapchat and
OL,9,Ffilmed him having what I believed to
OL,10,Fbe a seizure."
OL,12,FThe defendant said it was like
OL,13,Fprevious seizures and he filmed it to
OL,14,Fso he could show medical staff the
OL,15,Fsymptoms, and he did not think Preston
OL,16,Fneeded medical assistance at the time.
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@RO]pD@QOUrD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
