CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779642355
OL,3,CMurder accused denies lying over
OL,4,Cbaby's bath death
OL,6,FHe later flicked through his phone,
OL,7,Fdiscussing the online sale of a kayak,
OL,8,Flooked at social media and checked
OL,9,Femails as he soothed Preston who was
OL,10,Frecovering, he said.
OL,12,FThere was then two phone "activity
OL,13,Fgaps" lasting around a half an hour.
OL,15,FVarley said he ran a bath for the
OL,16,Fbaby, the water about two inches in
OL,17,Fdepth and he sat the child on a bath
OL,18,Fseat, as he got in the shower cubicle
OL,19,Fnext to it.
OL,26,@tD@ZOUuD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779642355
OL,3,CMurder accused denies lying over
OL,4,Cbaby's bath death
OL,6,FAfter a quick shower he said he left
OL,7,Fthe bathroom to get a towel and
OL,8,Fclothes but when he returned, one or
OL,9,Ftwo minutes later, Preston was off his
OL,10,Fseat and in the water.
OL,12,FVarley said: "When I entered the
OL,13,Fbathroom my legs just felt like jelly.
OL,14,FI scooped him up as quickly as I
OL,15,Fcould, he gasped for a breath of air."
OL,17,FThe defendant said he initially
OL,18,Fregarded it as a "stupid close call"
OL,19,Fbut the child then began vomiting very
OL,20,Fheavily and his condition worsened.
OL,26,@tD@NOUwD@fO]zD@ROUzD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779642355
OL,3,CMurder accused denies lying over
OL,4,Cbaby's bath death
OL,6,F"That's when panic started to kick
OL,7,Fin," Varley said, who told the court
OL,8,Fhe put his fingers in the child's
OL,9,Fmouth as he thought he might be
OL,10,Fchoking.
OL,12,FAt this time McGowan-Fazakerley
OL,13,Freturned home from work and Preston
OL,14,Flost consciousness, Varley said, so
OL,15,Fthey rushed him to hospital.
OL,17,FMedics tried for an hour to revive the
OL,18,Fbaby but told Varley they could not
OL,19,Fsave his life.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@DO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
