OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779642355
OL,3,CMurder accused denies lying over
OL,4,Cbaby's bath death
OL,6,FVarley continued: "I remember running
OL,7,Fstraight through them down the
OL,8,Fcorridors to see Preston.
OL,10,F"I remember at some point seeing a
OL,11,Fcross in the hospital, I remember
OL,12,Fgrabbing that cross asking the Lord
OL,13,Fnot to take him.
OL,15,F"I believe it was my fault through
OL,16,Fwalking out of the bathroom.
OL,18,F"At that point I did not know he had
OL,19,Fnot drowned."
OL,26,@nD@SOUrD@AOUwD@AOUzD@AOU{D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/14
