OL,3,CMurder accused denies lying over
OL,4,Cbaby's bath death
OL,6,FVarley denied ever having sexually or
OL,7,Fphysically abused the baby.
OL,9,FEarlier, Dr Alison Armour, who carried
OL,10,Fout a post-mortem examination, found
OL,11,Fnon-accidental, internal and external
OL,12,Finjuries.
OL,14,FShe gave the cause of death as acute
OL,15,Fupper airways obstruction by either
OL,16,Fsmothering or an object or objects
OL,17,Finserted into his mouth.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
