CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779642355
OL,3,CMurder accused denies lying over
OL,4,Cbaby's bath death
OL,6,FThe jury has heard Preston had
OL,7,Finternal injuries to his deep throat,
OL,8,Fbladder and bottom and "in excess" of
OL,9,F30 bruises and a human bite mark on
OL,10,Fhis right buttock.
OL,12,FParts of his anatomy were described as
OL,13,F"abnormal", with some injuries
OL,14,Fconsistent with "forcible penetration"
OL,15,Fand clinical signs of sexual abuse.
OL,26,@pD@XOUpD@bO]uD@AOUuD@JO]vD@QOUvD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/14
